两组之间的ESAT-6/CFP-10特异性IFN-γ水平没有显着差异。 </p><p xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:p1="http://pubmed.gov/pub-one">结论：使用LTBI和活性PTB区分与潜伏期相关的MTB抗原引起的MTB抗原引起的细胞因子谱的模式。特别是，IFN-γ和MDP-1，TNF-α和ACR以及IL-10和ACR的组合是有希望的。这项研究提供了WBS中MDP-1特异性细胞因子反应的实用性的首次证明。</p><p style="color: lightgray"> PMID： <a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/38665909/?utm_source=Chrome&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=journals&utm_content=101560960&ff=20240426081426&v=2.18.0.post9+e462414">38665909</a> | PMC： <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/PMC11044679/?utm_source=Chrome&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=journals&utm_content=101560960&ff=20240426081426&v=2.18.0.post9+e462414">PMC11044679</a> | doi： <a href=https://doi.org/10.3389/fimmu.2024.1330796>10.3389/fimmu.2024.1330796</a></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><guid ispermalink="false"> PubMed：38665909</guid><pubDate> Fri, 26 Apr 2024 06:00:00 -0400</pubDate><dc:creator> Ikkoh Yasuda</dc:creator><dc:creator> Naomi Ruth D Saludar</dc:creator><dc:creator>安娜·里亚·赛奥（Ana Ria Sayo）</dc:creator><dc:creator> Shuichi Suzuki</dc:creator><dc:creator> Akira Yokoyama</dc:creator><dc:creator> Yuriko Ozeki</dc:creator><dc:creator>小林遥</dc:creator><dc:creator>Akihito Nishiyama</dc:creator><dc:creator> Sohkichi Matsumoto</dc:creator><dc:creator>沙龙·考克斯（Sharon E Cox）</dc:creator><dc:creator>田中的田</dc:creator><dc:creator>Yoshiro Yamashita</dc:creator><dc:date> 2024-04-26</dc:date><dc:source>免疫学前沿</dc:source><dc:title>使用菲律宾的全血分析的结核分枝杆菌&lt;/em>;潜在抗原的细胞因子曲线评估</dc:title><dc:identifier>PMID：38665909</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> PMC：PMC11044679</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> doi：10.3389/fimmu.2024.1330796</dc:identifier></item></channel></rss>